                        <interp inst="t18761023-name-78" type="surname" value="COUSINS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18761023-name-78" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN COUSINS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman</hi>). I took the prisoner and found on him a railway ticket from Snow Hill to the Borough, a knife, and 4 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I am innocent. I was not near him.</p>
